"the man-made course\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A 12:21 opening lap would be followed by six more repetitions of the course, with Lecomte leading the quartet over the start/finish line until Pieterse decided to up the pace on the climb, causing Stigger to start dropping.\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4238, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A 12:21 opening lap\", \"from\": 4015, \"to\": 4034}, {\"ngram\": \"six more repetitions\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4076}, {\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4090}, {\"ngram\": \"Lecomte\", \"from\": 4097, \"to\": 4104}, {\"ngram\": \"the quartet\", \"from\": 4113, \"to\": 4124}, {\"ngram\": \"the start/finish line\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4151}, {\"ngram\": \"Pieterse\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4166}, {\"ngram\": \"the climb\", \"from\": 4193, \"to\": 4202}, {\"ngram\": \"Stigger\", \"from\": 4212, \"to\": 4219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutchwoman was countered by what would eventually be the race-winning move, as Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot switched into a huge gear and ate up the metres to crest the climb with a big gap on her compatriot Lecomte and Pieterse.\", \"from\": 4240, \"to\": 4459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Dutchwoman\", \"from\": 4240, \"to\": 4254}, {\"ngram\": \"the race-winning move\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4318}, {\"ngram\": \"Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot\", \"from\": 4323, \"to\": 4337}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge gear\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4363}, {\"ngram\": \"the metres\", \"from\": 4375, \"to\": 4385}, {\"ngram\": \"the climb\", \"from\": 4395, \"to\": 4404}, {\"ngram\": \"a big gap\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4419}, {\"ngram\": \"her compatriot\", \"from\": 4423, \"to\": 4437}, {\"ngram\": \"Lecomte\", \"from\": 4438, \"to\": 4445}, {\"ngram\": \"Pieterse\", \"from\": 4450, \"to\": 4458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot continued her assault to the delight of the French crowds, extending what was an 18-second gap at the first split point on lap two, out to 29 and 35 seconds respectively over Pieterse and Lecomte as she started lap three.\", \"from\": 4461, \"to\": 4697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4520, \"end\": 4526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9959164467679162, \"rank\": 0.0033895027444601237, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot\", \"from\": 4461, \"to\": 4475}, {\"ngram\": \"her assault\", \"from\": 4486, \"to\": 4497}, {\"ngram\": \"the delight\", \"from\": 4501, \"to\": 4512}, {\"ngram\": \"an 18-second gap\", \"from\": 4554, \"to\": 4570}, {\"ngram\": \"the first split point\", \"from\": 4574, \"to\": 4595}, {\"ngram\": \"lap\", \"from\": 4599, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"35 seconds\", \"from\": 4622, \"to\": 4632}, {\"ngram\": \"Pieterse\", \"from\": 4651, \"to\": 4659}, {\"ngram\": \"Lecomte\", \"from\": 4664, \"to\": 4671}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After completing lap two in an infernal time of 11:45, Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot followed this up with a 12:09 to extend her gap out north of a minute to her two chasers.\", \"from\": 4699, \"to\": 4858, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lap\", \"from\": 4716, \"to\": 4719}, {\"ngram\": \"an infernal time\", \"from\": 4727, \"to\": 4743}, {\"ngram\": \"Ferrand-Pr\\u00e9vot\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4768}, {\"ngram\": \"her gap\", \"from\": 4809, \"to\": 4816}, {\"ngram\": \"a minute\", \"from\": 4830, \"to\": 4838}, {\"ngram\": \"her two chasers\", \"from\": 4842, \"to\": 4857}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The race for bronze and silver was closing down behind as Batten came into her own on the second and third lap alongside Stigger and Rissveds, crossing the line at the start of lap four just 17 seconds back on a faltering Lecomte.\", \"from\": 4860, \"to\": 5090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The race\", \"from\": 